body.raw:
{
  "contents": [
    {
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are a recipe parser. Extract structured data from this recipe image.

Return ONLY valid JSON matching this schema:
{
  "title": "string",
  "yield": number or null,
  "prepTimeMinutes": number or null,
  "cookTimeMinutes": number or null,
  "ingredients": [{
    "quantity": number or null,
    "unit": "string or null (normalize to: cup, tbsp, tsp, oz, lb, g, kg, ml, l, piece, pinch, dash)",
    "item": "string (the ingredient name)",
    "preparation": "string or null",
    "rawText": "string (exact text from image)"
  }],
  "instructions": [{
    "stepNumber": number,
    "instruction": "string",
    "rawText": "string"
  }]
}

Rules:
- Normalize units (tablespoon → tbsp, teaspoon → tsp)
- Convert fractions to decimals (1/2 → 0.5)
- Separate preparation notes from ingredient names
- Number instructions sequentially
- If information is unclear, use null"
        },
        {
          "inline_data": {
            "mime_type": "image/png",
            "data": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=="
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "generationConfig": {
    "response_mime_type": "application/json"
  }
}

request.description:
Send a recipe image to Gemini API for parsing. The model will extract recipe information and return it as JSON.

Expected response:
```json
{
  "candidates": [
    {
      "content": {
        "parts": [
          {
            "text": "{json response with parsed recipe}"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

